WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:01.000 --> 00:00:03.067
 Load the model data of Poser into modo and render it. 

00:00:03.567 --> 00:00:06.518
 Press the "delete" key to delete the "Andy" figure. 

00:00:07.018 --> 00:00:12.531
 Load "Ryan Casual" from the library. 

00:00:13.031 --> 00:00:17.583
 Choose File menu&gt; Export&gt; Wavefront OBJ ... 

00:00:18.083 --> 00:00:20.189
 Confirm that "Export range" is set to single frame, and click "OK" button. 

00:00:20.689 --> 00:00:24.292
 Uncheck the floor in "Select Object" and press "OK" button. 

00:00:24.792 --> 00:00:27.421
 Clear all the "Export" check boxes and press the "OK" button. 

00:00:27.921 --> 00:00:38.342
 Press the "Save" button as the file name is ryan.obj. 

00:00:38.842 --> 00:00:43.166
 Choose File menu&gt; Export&gt; COLLADA | RWY. 

00:00:43.666 --> 00:00:45.163
 Confirm that "Export range" is set to single frame, and click "OK" button. 

00:00:45.663 --> 00:00:49.749
 Uncheck the floor in "Select Object" and press "OK" button. 

00:00:50.249 --> 00:00:57.583
 Press the "Save" button with the file name as ryan.dae. 

00:00:58.083 --> 00:01:06.839
 By default, the export option will press the OK button. ※ COLLADA export is done to export the image file used for the texture. 

00:01:07.339 --> 00:01:10.846
 Switch to modo. 

00:01:11.346 --> 00:01:17.580
 Select ryan.obj with File&gt; Open and press the "Open" button. 

00:01:28.544 --> 00:01:42.227
 The file has been read. I zoom in and check it. 

00:01:42.727 --> 00:01:52.499
 The eye and eyelash texture is not applied, so set it manually. 

00:01:52.999 --> 00:02:14.624
 Apply eyelash texture from drag and drop from Finder. 

00:02:15.124 --> 00:02:32.240
 Apply the eye texture as well. 

00:02:32.740 --> 00:02:33.927
 As the material of the band is black, I correct it. 

00:02:34.427 --> 00:02:40.749
 Change the selection mode to material, and select a band. ※ A pop-up is displayed when you right-click the item button. 

00:02:41.549 --> 00:02:45.896
 Select Material in the shader tree. 

00:02:46.396 --> 00:03:04.152
 Increase the amount of transparency of the material (transparency) in the property. 

00:03:04.652 --> 00:03:27.918
 Change the texture of the eyelashes to transparency in the shader tree. ※ pop-up is displayed when you right-click. 

00:03:28.418 --> 00:03:43.721
 Press the rendering tab to switch layouts and check in the preview rendering. 

00:03:44.521 --> 00:03:46.304
 As the eyes are black, adjust the material. 

00:03:46.804 --> 00:03:53.612
 Right-click on the preview render and select a material. 

00:03:54.112 --> 00:03:59.628
 Adjust the diffuse amount in the property material (reflection). 

00:04:00.128 --> 00:04:11.531
 Adjust the other eye as well. 

00:04:13.523 --> 00:04:17.833
 Apply the appropriate environment from Enviroment of the preset library by double click. 

00:04:18.333 --> 00:04:23.048
 Select Render in the shader tree. 

00:04:23.548 --> 00:04:28.207
 Select global lighting for properties and enable indirect lighting. 

00:04:28.707 --> 00:04:41.493
 It's a bit too bright, so reduce the emission of Directional Light. 

00:04:55.270 --> 00:05:15.094
 Mostly good. Choose Render&gt; Render and try rendering. 

